The paper primarily focuses on security challenges in mobile web services, which falls under the category of "Computer Security and Cryptography" (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper also discusses the state-of-the-art security awareness in wired and wireless web services, which can be categorized under "Software Engineering" (cs.SE) and "Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing" (cs.DC). The paper also addresses performance analysis results, which can be classified under "Networking and Internet Architecture" (cs.NI) and "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS).
